Date: Sat, 07 Jun 2003 20:33:18 +0530
From: Satadal Das <drsatdas@hotmail.com>

6 more persons died due to this mysterious disease leading to a total
toll of 36 persons. All of them were children except 5 [presumably
this refers to 5 out of the total of 36 persons - Mod.MPP]. Senior
health personnel said scorching summer heat might be a contributory
factor. Investigations are ongoing.
--
From: Dr. Satadal Das, MD, DCP
